{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_29","type":"agent_message","text":"Human intervention needed\n\nThe automated job failed for `org.apache.maven:maven-settings-builder:3.0`.\n\nPreserved work branch: https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/tree/ai%2Fvjovanov%2Fhuman-intervention%2Fissue-2377-library-new-request-org.apache.maven-maven-settings-builder-3.0-b95dbe6d\n\nThe preserved work suggests test generation mostly succeeded and the final blocker was the Gradle/native-image stage, not metadata discovery. The clearest evidence is in `logs/org.apache.maven:maven-settings-builder:3.0/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-12T18-18-07-490608Z.log` and `logs/org.apache.maven:maven-settings-builder:3.0/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-12T18-18-59-392190Z.log`, where `:nativeTestCompile` fails with `Fatal error: Unable to create temp directory for prefix driverRoot-: java.nio.file.FileSystemException: No space left on device`. Earlier retries also hit temp-dir exhaustion during `:test` in `logs/org.apache.maven:maven-settings-builder:3.0/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-12T18-16-56-905657Z.log`, and one intermediate run had a real assertion mismatch in `validatorCollectsErrorsAndWarningsForInvalidSettings()` in `logs/org.apache.maven:maven-settings-builder:3.0/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-12T18-17-36-239811Z.log`, but the preserved test results now show `9` tests and `0` failures in `tests/src/org.apache.maven/maven-settings-builder/3.0/build/test-results/test/TEST-org_apache_maven.maven_settings_builder.Maven_settings_builderTest.xml`, so that assertion issue appears to have been fixed before preservation.\n\nUseful files to inspect are `logs/org.apache.maven:maven-settings-builder:3.0/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-05-12T18-16-56-861993Z.log`, the four `logs/org.apache.maven:maven-settings-builder:3.0/gradle-test/*.log` files above, and `tests/src/org.apache.maven/maven-settings-builder/3.0/build/reports/dynamic-access/dynamic-access-coverage.json` (the preserved report shows `hasDynamicAccess=false` and `0/0` calls). The preserved metadata file is also currently `{}` at `metadata/org.apache.maven/maven-settings-builder/3.0/reachability-metadata.json`.\n\nManual next steps:\n1. Re-run the library with enough free temp space, or force Native Image to use a writable temp directory, then run `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=org.apache.maven:maven-settings-builder:3.0`.\n2. Review the preserved branch and decide whether to keep or drop the added `build.gradle` temp-dir workaround, since `nativeTestCompile` still failed after it was added.\n3. If the rerun passes, verify whether empty metadata (`{}`) plus `0/0` dynamic-access coverage is acceptable for this library before proceeding."}}
